/27/adding-real-time-to-a-restful-rails-app/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Adding Real-Time to a RESTful Rails App</a></li> <li><a href=\"http://instagram-engineering.tumblr.com/post/40781627982/handling-growth-with-postgres-5-tips-from-instagram\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">5 хинтов при работе с PostgreSQL от Instagram</a></li> </ul> <h2 id=\"javascript\">JavaScript</h2> <ul> <li><a href=\"http://paulirish.com/2013/webkit-for-developers/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">WebKit для разработчиков</a></li> <li>Релиз <a href=\"http://coffeescript.org/#literate\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Coffeescript 1.5 c Literate</a>\n</li> <li>Релиз <a href=\"http://foundation.zurb.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Foundation 4</a>. <a href=\"http://foundation.zurb.com/migration.php\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Миграция c 3</a>\n</li> <li><a href=\"http://bombermine.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Bombermine на AngularJS</a></li> <li><a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/user/W3Conf/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Видео с W3Conf</a></li> </ul> <p></p>\n</body></html>\n","date":"Fri, 01 Mar 2013 00:00:00 +0200","human_date":"01.03.2013","link":"https://www.rwpod.com/posts/2013/03/01/podcast-01-04.html","main_img":"https://www.rwpod.com/images/static/01/0104.png","audio_url":"https://mp3.rwpod-assets.com/podcasts/01/0104.mp3","audio_file_size":17213728,"audio_type":"audio/mpeg","audio_duration":"00:17:52"},{"id":"31c33fc10e15ab3c02dd1730ec34defcdb5c6f911f5aaa4a48e692f67f6e1f25","title":"03 выпуск 01 сезона. Ruby 20 лет и релиз версии 2.0.0, MoSQL, k-d деревья, и прочее","summary":"\n\nДобрый день уважаемые сл...","description":"<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0 Transitional//EN\" \"http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/loose.dtd\">\n<html><body>\n<p>Добрый день уважаемые слушатели. Представляем новый выпуск подкаста RWpod. В этом выпуске:</p> <h2 id=\"ruby\">Ruby</h2> <ul> <li>Релиз Ruby <a href=\"http://www.ruby-lang.org/en/news/2013/02/22/ruby-1-9-3-p392-is-released/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">1.9.3-p392</a> и <a href=\"http://www.ruby-lang.org/en/news/2013/02/24/ruby-2-0-0-p0-is-released/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">2.0.0-p0</a>. 23 февраля Ruby исполнилось 20 лет!</li> <li><a href=\"http://benediktdeicke.com/2013/02/what-you-did-not-know-about-capistrano-yet/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Чего вы могли не знать о Capistrano</a></li> <li><a href=\"http://blog.envylabs.com/post/43076921318/rails-4-routing-concerns\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Rails 4.0 routing concerns</a></li> <li><a href=\"https://github.com/stripe/mosql\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">MongoDB PostgreSQL репликация</a></li> <li><a href=\"http://spin.atomicobject.com/2013/02/15/ffi-foreign-function-interfaces/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">FFI</a></li> <li><a href=\"http://csolg.com/blogs/nastroika-rezervnogo-arhivirovaniya-backup-ruby-on-rails-32-proektov\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Настройка резервного архивирования Ruby on Rails 3.2 проектов</a></li> <li><a href=\"https://github.com/igor-alexandrov/wiselinks\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Wiselinks gem</a></li> <li><a href=\"http://alindeman.github.com/2013/02/18/decoding-rails-session-cookies.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Декомпиляция сессионных кук в Rails 3</a></li> <li><a href=\"https://github.com/colinsurprenant/geokdtree\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Geokdtree - k-d дерево для Ruby</a></li> <li><a href=\"https://github.com/apeiros/sorting\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Sorting gem</a></li> <li><a href=\"http://rails-sqli.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ActiveRecord не безопасные методы</a></li> </ul> <h2 id=\"javascript\">JavaScript</h2> <ul> <li><